name: AI-Develop RAG pipeline using SQL database in Fabric
description:
Use this Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) data pipeline template to get your data ready in SQL Database in fabric for building Generative AI and Agentic AI applications. 

 Triggered by Azure Blob Storage events, the pipeline copies the file to the Lakehouse, extracts the content from the file, chunks the content, redacts any PII information, generates embeddings, and stores the chunks and embeddings in SQL Database in Fabric.

 As a part of configuring the pipeline, you will be required to provide values for predefined variables such as "apiKey", "cognitiveServiceEndpoint", "openAIEndpoint", "openAIKey" etc., by selecting the pipeline canvas and navigating to the variables menu. Additionally, the pipeline configuration will also depend on  Python Notebook and UserDataFunction. 

The source files and documentation for this pipeline can  can be found at:
 https://github.com/Azure-Samples/fabric-sqldb-ai-ragpipeline
author: sqlgenai@microsoft.com
